dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.swcomponenttemplate.swcinternalbehavior.trigger

Interface IInternalTriggeringPoint

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAbstractAccessPoint, IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable

    public interface IInternalTriggeringPoint
extends IEntity, IAbstractAccessPoint
    IInternalTriggeringPoint: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    If a RunnableEntity owns an InternalTriggeringPoint it is entitled to trigger the execution of RunnableEntities of the corresponding software-component.
